translations: n.兰巴达（一种巴西贴身舞）

phrs.translation: 兰巴达, 伦巴达, 拉丁舞曲, 森巴热潮

sentences.sentence: Lambada, a fast modern dance originally from Brazil, also named dance next to skin.
sentences.translation: 兰巴达，源自巴西的快步现代舞，也叫贴身舞。
